平</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有1個方法係如果你喇叭有2個輸入<br />\n你可以淘寶買個光纖轉紅白線<br />\n由ps4光纖直出喇叭"},{"pid":"1542eff8a8e4f67fd9eb11afe6c6e225345e799e","tid":440232,"uid":141573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T04:59:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1)買個有aux 同toslink輸入的amp <br />\n2)買個hdmi 2入1出<br />\n3)買多個speaker<br />\n4)買個有aux 輸入又有喇叭的mon<br />\n方法2最平</blockquote><br />\n唔明第二個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}